original_title: TV's Funniest Comedians - 14 Stars Do Classic Routines
overview: A compilation film of stand up performances and comedy routines featuring some of the biggest stars in the early years of television. This film was directed by Sandy Olivieri. Here is a partial list of the performers who appeared in the film Bob Newhart, Mort Sahl, Jack Benny, Lenny Bruce, Johnny Carson, George Carlin, et al.
title: TV's Funniest Comedians - 14 Stars Do Classic Routines
